{"tid":437113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成人網站PornHub藏「毒」！ 過百萬電腦遭受感染！！","createTime":"2017-10-15T16:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T17:28:55.000Z","uid":1886,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"12c73d00dcd1f5759a19f0c151d83a3e7cddf7d9","tid":437113,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕近日全球知名的成人網站PornHub，遭到資安公司Proofpoint發現，該網站中的Traffic Junky廣告藏有Kovter木馬病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並且藏身長達1年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，估計約上百萬人受害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。目前受害的國家有英國、美國、加拿大和澳大利亞等4國，而亞洲地區未傳出有受害的情形。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/10/15/1095518-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F1095518-XXL.jpg&h=1adaa8ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; 全球知名的成人網站PornHub，遭到資安公司Proofpoint發現，廣告中藏有Kovter木馬病毒，估計高達數百萬的受害者。</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2222716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2222716&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2982dfe8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2222716&h=74cc4a67\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2222716</a></div>"},{"pid":"f221af2bbfc7c47d2f1335eaad1e639b1a366665","tid":437113,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"據《堪薩斯城星報》指出，統計網站流量的Alexa公司指出，PornHub在美國排名是第20名，全球第37名。估計每天有8000萬人次瀏覽，並可能有數百萬人的電腦已經遭到感染。<br />\n<br />\n針對Kovter病毒一事，PornHub官方目前為止並未正面回應，但Proofpoint公司表示，PornHub已接獲通知，並立即刪除Kovter病毒。他們也表示，受害國家包括英國、美國、加拿大和澳大利亞等4國。<br />\n<br />\n目前未傳出台灣或華人使用者有受害的情形，但仍不可掉以輕心。有PPT網友爆掛分享資訊，引起網友搞笑回應，「好險我都看色情守門員」、「好險我不喜歡看歐美片」、「mac看的路過」。<br />\n<br />\n如果擔心是否中Kovter，可以參考以下連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/virus-removal/remove-kovter-trojan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bleepingcomputer.com%2Fvirus-removal%2Fremove-kovter-trojan&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ee5b2d2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/virus-removal/remove-kovter-trojan</a>"},{"pid":"69b64c9d46dcfd98f3652ca95b240b56ed22ae35","tid":437113,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"根據綜合媒體報導指出，該病毒常見的模式是當 Windows使用者以「IE」與「Edge」瀏覽Pornhub時，會跳出要求更新Flash的視窗，而使用「Chrome」或「Firefox」瀏覽時則會出現要求瀏覽器更新的訊息。只要使用者點擊該視窗，將會啟動蠕蟲病毒Kovte的下載，而該病毒會長時間存在於使用者的電腦中，讓駭客得以用該電腦的點擊廣告賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=304732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D304732&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a67d9079\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D304732&h=f6d20ed7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=304732</a>"},{"pid":"a6dd8b5e526678c1e3f4b32ed40eda362e34b921","tid":437113,"uid":133533,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"出得黎行，怕甚麼"},{"pid":"d17048549abe033dc578b9b7d22a62be6d9cfebc","tid":437113,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"又話咸網係最安全既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc016dccf8fa881d01ee95577996792ec5e35d5","tid":437113,"uid":148994,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依家可能開咗有花柳病毒，先有大迴響"},{"pid":"3c00327860a78d82e396020e5a8c929523bcbcb1","tid":437113,"uid":53027,"like":24,"dislike":3,"sc